short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a New Dashboard Of Bookmarks and Override the Chrome Newtab page.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Personalized Bookmark Dashboard for Chrome's New Tab!

Enhance your browsing experience by creating a personalized dashboard for your bookmarks, replacing the default Chrome New Tab page. This feature allows you to curate and organize your favorite sites in a sleek, visually appealing layout. Easily access your most-used websites with custom categories, thumbnails, and dynamic updates. Stay organized, productive, and in control of your online experience every time you open a new tab!
